# React Admin Panel Architecture — AutoBid (Cars Buy & Sell)

> **Generated from**: React Native Expo project `Asset-Manager` (app name: **AutoBid**)
> **Brand**: Raj Motors — "Driving Deals, Funding Dreams"

---

## Part 1 — React Native Project Analysis

### 1.1 Complete Folder Structure

```
Asset-Manager/
├── app/                          # Expo Router (file-based routing)
