### 1.2 Project Architecture

| Aspect | Details |
|---|---|
| **Framework** | React Native + Expo SDK 54 |
| **Routing** | Expo Router v6 (file-based, Stack + Tabs) |
| **State Management** | React Context API ([AuthContext](file:///c:/Users/ganup/Downloads/Asset-Manager%20%281%29/Asset-Manager/contexts/AuthContext.tsx#19-28)) + React Query (`@tanstack/react-query`) + local state |
| **API Client** | Custom `fetch` wrapper ([apiRequest](file:///c:/Users/ganup/Downloads/Asset-Manager%20%281%29/Asset-Manager/lib/query-client.ts#27-45), [apiRequestDirect](file:///c:/Users/ganup/Downloads/Asset-Manager%20%281%29/Asset-Manager/lib/auth.ts#102-125)) — no Axios |
| **Data Fetching** | React Query for declarative queries ([deals.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ganup/Downloads/Asset-Manager%20%281%29/Asset-Manager/app/%28tabs%29/deals.tsx)), manual `fetch` for imperative calls |
| **Auth Flow** | JWT + Refresh Token → SecureStore (mobile) / localStorage (web) |
| **User Status Flow** | `PENDING_PHONE` → `PENDING_EMAIL` → `PENDING_APPROVAL` → `ACCEPTED` / `REJECTED` / `BLOCKED` |
| **Verification** | Phone OTP → Email OTP → Admin approval |
| **Typography** | Google Fonts — **Urbanist** (400 Regular, 500 Medium, 600 SemiBold, 700 Bold) |
| **ORM** | Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL ([shared/schema.ts](file:///c:/Users/ganup/Downloads/Asset-Manager%20%281%29/Asset-Manager/shared/schema.ts)) |
| **Other libs** | Zustand (installed but unused), dayjs, expo-haptics, expo-image, react-hook-form |

