### 1.5 API Endpoints

**Base URL**: `http://192.168.1.102:8002` (user service), `http://192.168.1.102:8000` (auth service)

#### Authentication APIs (port 8000)

| Method | Route | Description | Auth |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/auth/signin` | Login with email/phone + password | No |
| `POST` | `/auth/signup` | Register new user | No |

#### User Service APIs (port 8002)

| Method | Route | Description | Auth |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/user/home` | Home page (featured, recent, categories) | No |
| `GET` | `/user/listings?type=AUCTION` | Live auction listings | No |
| `GET` | `/user/listings?type=BUY_NOW` | Buy-now listings | No |
| `GET` | `/user/listings/:id` | Listing detail by ID | No |
| `POST` | `/user/listings/:id/bid` | Place bid on auction | Yes |
| `POST` | `/user/listings/:id/buy` | Purchase buy-now listing | Yes |
| `GET` | `/user/users-profile` | Get user profile | Yes |
| `PUT` | `/user/users-profile` | Update user profile (name, gender) | Yes |
| `POST` | `/user/user-device` | Register device (FCM, tokens) | No |
| `POST` | `/user/sell-request` | Submit vehicle for sale | Yes |

#### Mock Server APIs (Express — development)

| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register` | Register user |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/verify-phone` | Verify phone OTP |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/verify-email` | Verify email OTP |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/resend-otp` | Resend OTP |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/request-otp` | Request login OTP |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/verify-phone-otp` | Verify login OTP |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/demo-login` | Demo login |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/logout` | Logout |
| `GET` | `/api/user/home` | Home data |
| `GET` | `/api/user/live` | Live auctions |
| `POST` | `/api/user/live/:id/bid` | Place bid |
| `GET` | `/api/user/buy-now` | Buy-now listings |
| `POST` | `/api/user/buy-now/:id/purchase` | Purchase listing |
| `GET` | `/api/user/deals` | User deals |
| `GET` | `/api/user/profile` | User profile |
| `GET` | `/api/subscriptions/me` | Current subscription |
| `POST` | `/api/subscriptions/purchase` | Subscribe to plan |
| `POST` | `/api/user/sell-request` | Sell request |

