## Part 2 — React Admin Panel Design

### 2.1 Recommended Tech Stack

| Category | Technology | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| **Framework** | React 19 + Vite 6 | Matches mobile's React 19; fast HMR |
| **Language** | TypeScript 5.x | Type-safe, matches mobile codebase |
| **Routing** | React Router v7 | Mature, supports nested + protected routes |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS v4 (per user spec) | Rapid UI development, consistent design |
| **Data Fetching** | TanStack React Query v5 | Same library as mobile app, shared patterns |
| **HTTP Client** | Axios | Request/response interceptors, cleaner API |
| **State Management** | Zustand | Already installed in mobile project, lightweight |
| **Forms** | React Hook Form + Zod | Already in mobile deps, type-safe validation |
| **UI Library** | shadcn/ui components | Headless, Tailwind-native, fully customizable |
| **Charts** | Recharts | Dashboard analytics & reporting |
| **Tables** | TanStack Table v8 | Feature-rich data tables with pagination |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Consistent with shadcn/ui ecosystem |
| **Dates** | dayjs | Same as mobile project |
| **Notifications** | Sonner (toast) | Clean, modern toast notifications |

