### 2.3 Admin Modules — Detailed Breakdown

#### 🏠 Dashboard

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Page** | `pages/dashboard/index.tsx` |
| **Stats Cards** | Total Users, Active Listings, Live Auctions, Monthly Revenue, Pending Approvals, Deals This Week |
| **Charts** | Revenue trend (line), Listings by category (pie), Deals by status (bar), User registrations (area) |
| **Quick Info** | Recent sell requests, Active auctions ending soon, Pending user approvals |
| **API** | `GET /admin/dashboard/stats`, `GET /admin/dashboard/charts` |

#### 👥 User Management

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Pages** | List (`pages/users/index.tsx`), Detail/Edit (`pages/users/[id].tsx`) |
| **Table Columns** | Avatar, Name, Email, Phone, Status (badge), Registration Date, Actions |
| **CRUD** | View, Edit profile, Change status (Approve/Reject/Block), Delete |
| **Filters** | By status (`PENDING_APPROVAL`, `ACCEPTED`, `REJECTED`, `BLOCKED`), search by name/email/phone |
| **Status Actions** | Approve pending users, Block/Unblock users, Reject registrations |
| **API** | `GET /admin/users`, `GET /admin/users/:id`, `PUT /admin/users/:id`, `PUT /admin/users/:id/status`, `DELETE /admin/users/:id` |

#### 🚗 Listing Management

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Pages** | List (`pages/listings/index.tsx`), Detail/Edit (`pages/listings/[id].tsx`), Create (`pages/listings/create.tsx`) |
| **Table Columns** | Image thumbnail, Title, Type (badge), Category, Price, Bid Count, Status, Seller, Actions |
| **CRUD** | Create new listing, Edit details, Change status, Delete listing |
| **Filters** | By type (AUCTION/BUY_NOW), category, status, price range, date range |
| **API** | `GET /admin/listings`, `POST /admin/listings`, `GET /admin/listings/:id`, `PUT /admin/listings/:id`, `DELETE /admin/listings/:id` |

#### ⚡ Live Auction Management

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Pages** | List (`pages/auctions/index.tsx`), Detail (`pages/auctions/[id].tsx`) |
| **Features** | View all active auctions, see bid history, extend/end auctions, monitor countdown |
| **Real-time** | Auto-refresh, live bid count updates |
| **API** | `GET /admin/auctions`, `GET /admin/auctions/:id/bids`, `PUT /admin/auctions/:id/extend`, `PUT /admin/auctions/:id/end` |

#### 📋 Sell Request Management

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Pages** | List (`pages/sell-requests/index.tsx`), Detail (`pages/sell-requests/[id].tsx`) |
| **Features** | Review seller submissions, approve/reject with notes, convert to listing |
| **Table Columns** | Title, Seller, Category, Listing Type, Base Price, Status, Submitted Date, Actions |
| **Status Flow** | `PENDING_ADMIN_REVIEW` → `APPROVED` (creates listing) / `REJECTED` |
| **API** | `GET /admin/sell-requests`, `PUT /admin/sell-requests/:id/approve`, `PUT /admin/sell-requests/:id/reject` |

#### 🤝 Deals / Transactions

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Pages** | List (`pages/deals/index.tsx`), Detail (`pages/deals/[id].tsx`) |
| **Table** | Vehicle, Buyer, Type, Price, Status, Date, Payment Status |
| **Status Badges** | WON (green), PENDING_PAYMENT (amber), COMPLETED (blue), LOST (gray) |
| **API** | `GET /admin/deals`, `GET /admin/deals/:id`, `PUT /admin/deals/:id/status` |

#### 📂 Category Management

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Page** | `pages/categories/index.tsx` |
| **CRUD** | Create, rename, delete categories |
| **Data** | Sedan, SUV, Hatchback, Luxury, Sports, Electric (from mobile) |
| **API** | `GET /admin/categories`, `POST /admin/categories`, `PUT /admin/categories/:id`, `DELETE /admin/categories/:id` |

#### 💳 Subscription Management

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Page** | `pages/subscriptions/index.tsx` |
| **Features** | View all user subscriptions, manage plans, modify pricing |
| **Plans** | Basic (₹499/2 listings), Standard (₹999/4 listings), Premium (₹1999/10 listings) |
| **API** | `GET /admin/subscriptions`, `PUT /admin/subscriptions/:id` |

#### 📊 Reports & Analytics

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Page** | `pages/reports/index.tsx` |
| **Charts** | Revenue over time, listings created vs sold, top categories, user growth, auction performance |
| **Exports** | CSV/PDF export functionality |
| **API** | `GET /admin/reports/revenue`, `GET /admin/reports/listings`, `GET /admin/reports/users` |

#### ⚙️ Settings

| Item | Details |
|---|---|
| **Page** | `pages/settings/index.tsx` |
| **Sections** | App config, Default subscription plans pricing, Email/SMS templates, Admin profile |

